    <entry>
      <title>Reference on Building a Hexo Blog</title>
      <link href="/2019/06/13/Introduction/"/>
      <url>/2019/06/13/Introduction/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Introduction"><a href="#Introduction" class="headerlink" title="Introduction"></a>Introduction</h1><p>Welcome to my blog, this is my first post, thanks to the tutorial on how to build a blog with Hexo and the open-source themes.</p><p>The following tutorial links are Chinese.</p><h2 id="Create-a-blog-using-hexo"><a href="#Create-a-blog-using-hexo" class="headerlink" title="Create a blog using hexo"></a>Create a blog using hexo</h2><p>Tutorial Link: <a href="https://my.oschina.net/ryaneLee/blog/638440">Tutorial on how to build your own blog with Hexo</a></p><h2 id="Useful-Hexo-Commands"><a href="#Useful-Hexo-Commands" class="headerlink" title="Useful Hexo Commands"></a>Useful Hexo Commands</h2><ul><li>Clean caches (e.g. when changing themes): <code>hexo clean</code></li><li>Generate pages: <code>hexo generate</code> / <code>hexo g</code></li><li>Check Locally: <code>hexo server</code></li><li>Deploy on GitHub Page: <code>hexo deploy</code> / <code>hexo d</code></li><li>Or just use: <code>hexo g -d</code></li><li>Create new page: <code>hexo new page &quot;new page&#39;s title&quot;</code></li><li>Create new post: <code>hexo new post &quot;new post&#39;s title&quot;</code></li></ul><h2 id="Hexo-Theme-Recommendation"><a href="#Hexo-Theme-Recommendation" class="headerlink" title="Hexo Theme Recommendation"></a>Hexo Theme Recommendation</h2><ul><li><a href="https://demo.jerryc.me/">Theme: butterfly (currently in use, based on melody)</a></li><li><a href="https://github.com/Molunerfinn/hexo-theme-melody">Theme: melody</a></li></ul><h2 id="How-to-let-your-blog-got-searched-on-Baidu-amp-Google"><a href="#How-to-let-your-blog-got-searched-on-Baidu-amp-Google" class="headerlink" title="How to let your blog got searched on Baidu &amp; Google"></a>How to let your blog got searched on Baidu &amp; Google</h2><p>Tutorial Link: <a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/25145964abf3">Tutorial on how to add your blog in Google &amp; Baidu</a></p><p>Another tutorial: <a href="http://tengj.github.io/2016/03/14/hexo6seo/">Tutorial on how to add your blog in Google &amp; Baidu</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
